        <div class="reviewText stacked">
              <span id="reviewTextContainer3819030783" class="readable"
              >
            
<span id="freeTextContainer8792089933547649690">This was my first Woodiwiss historical. Shared it with my sister and my friends, it was that good!<br/>Years later, I tried to read it again and thought to myself: what was I so excited about?<br/>Still a great read, if somewhat tame by today&apos;s standards.</span>
  <span id="freeText8792089933547649690" style="display:none">This was my first Woodiwiss historical. Shared it with my sister and my friends, it was that good!<br />Years later, I tried to read it again and thought to myself: what was I so excited about?<br />Still a great read, if somewhat tame by today's standards.</span>
